3D models & CAD
====

CAD and printable files for the vehicle. Anyone should be able to reproduce
the chassis from the files here (rubric criterion 5: reproducibility).

Folders:
- AutoCAD/  — editable CAD source (chassis decks, mounts, linkage)
- STL/      — printable/exported meshes for the same parts

Suggested filenames:
- lower-deck.stl / .dwg
- upper-deck.stl / .dwg
- lidar-mount.stl
- servo-linkage.stl
- pi-mount.stl

Reference dimensions live in docs/Mechanical-Design.md and other/pinout.md
(wheel 44 mm, two-deck standoff frame).
